Enum Currency

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Currency>
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.intl.enums.Currency

    Serializable, Comparable<Currency>, Key, IsLocaleItem
    public enum Currency

    Enumerates the standard codes for script identification which can be used to create and manage locale.
